      },
      "lineNbr": 232,
      "author": {
        "id": 5120
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-06-26T14:51:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The new code introduces a new problem. In the same situation, you will now never process byParent[0], because len(byParent[0]) \u003d\u003d maxSliceSize will not be true on later iterations.\n\nMaybe it would be better to fail early if we see entities both with and without a parent.",
      "parentUuid": "ae7efb56_de7b9b78",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 231,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 232,
        "endChar": 21
      },
